TGLFEP_kwscale_scan.f90:          write(88,10)factor(ifactor),(g(n),f(n),keep_label(n),n=1,nmodes)
TGLFEP_kwscale_scan.f90:    if (fmark .lt. 1.0E10) then     ! accepted mode with all constraints
